rComments: I think she tries very hard to give good lectures. She is super helpful when I ask questions after class and very approachable. Looking back at the slides I think she put a lot of work into them. I found the class confusing and the lecture could be clearer still but it's math (and I suck at math) so I think it's not really her fault.

She reads off the slides, I don't think she's tried any math tests from UofT, doesn't do examples with students in class. Never writes stuff herself to help us understand. Doesn't really talk a lot of about the exam, just teaches the things she has to teach for the day. Not very helpful.
